'''Conner Ship Systems''' was a small arms manufacturing company that specialized in producing weapons including [[Conner net]]s and [[Space mine/Legends|space mines]].<ref name="EGWT">''[[The Essential Guide to Weapons and Technology]]''</ref> Among their products were the [[3HX3 timer mine|3HX3 repulsorlift mine]] and [[HX2 antipersonnel mine]]. Their best-known product, however, was the electrified starship-disabling "[[Conner net]]," a favorite of [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]] and defense forces alike.

